        "url": "https://code.visualstudio.com/License/"
    },
    "notes": [
        "üß© Visual Studio Code with NeonTowel's opinionated flavor!",
        "",
        "‚ú® Key extensions installed:",
        "  ‚Ä¢ Dev Containers     ‚Ä¢ WSL Remote",
