        "  ‚Ä¢ TOML Support       ‚Ä¢ Go",
        "  ‚Ä¢ Rust Analyzer      ‚Ä¢ Indent Rainbow",
        "  ‚Ä¢ Rainbow Brackets   ‚Ä¢ REST Client",
